title: 5 people, including 3 kids, found dead in Minnesota home
content:
Police say five people, including three children, are dead in a home in a western Minneapolis suburb in an apparent murder-suicide. 
 
South Lake Minnetonka Police Chief Mike Siitari tells KSTP-TV that police were called to the home when no one was seen or heard from for several days. Siitari says the children did not show up for school this week.
